---
title: Maple-Balsamic Glazed Pork Chops with Sweet Potato Mash and Feta
description: Traditional but with a twist. Maple, balsamic and pork are meant for each other, especially when served alongside roasted mashed sweet potatoes with a sprinkle of feta! Brussels sprouts are sautéed to crisp perfection, with an almond flourish that makes the dish really sing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cotelettes-de-porc-au-glacage-balsamique-et-a-lerable-39b6c506.jpg
